Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:42.10,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}10年先の未来が見える魔法があったらな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:42.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如果有能看到10年后未来的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:43.82,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}見上げた空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:43.82,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}望着天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:52.57,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}追いかけ続けるほど　逃げていく世界の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:52.57,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}继续追逐着 在消逝的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.84,0:00:57.18,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}悩まずいられるのにな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.84,0:00:57.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}没有烦恼的生存着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:02.11,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}時を切り裂くような速さで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:02.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}用撕裂时间的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:05.68,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}駆け抜けてく（駆け抜けてく）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:05.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}飞驰着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:08.77,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}流されてく（流されてく）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:08.77,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}流逝着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:12.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}空に揺られながら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:12.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一边在空中摇晃着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:19.90,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}僕らは飛び立とうとしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:19.90,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一边这样飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:24.81,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}さんざん見た未来地図と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:24.81,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}用力看到的未来地图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.07,0:01:31.44,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}折れた翼広げ　広げ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.07,0:01:31.44,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}展开折断的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:36.87,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今　始まろうとしてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:36.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}现在 即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:41.74,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}誰か呼ぶ声がする
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:41.74,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}什么人在呼唤着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:51.52,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\blur3}暁を染めて　染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:51.52,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\blur3}将黎明染色 染色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[ED]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:15.46,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君だけのため　光る世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:15.46,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只为你闪耀的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:20.75,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ここにあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:20.75,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.05,0:22:29.57,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}幼い手で握り締めてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.05,0:22:29.57,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}幼嫩的双手握住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:33.12,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}なくさないよう　ギュッと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:33.12,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}紧紧地握住 为了不失去它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:42.46,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}真っ白な願いを　君と追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:42.46,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}和你一起追逐 这纯白的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.85,0:22:50.57,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}また迷い込む　寂しげな夜だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.85,0:22:50.57,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}又再次迷失于这寂寞的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:56.02,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}あの日の面影を　見つけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:56.02,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}找出那天你的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.48,0:22:59.68,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}思い出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.48,0:22:59.68,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我会想起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.26,0:23:04.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君がいるから　どこでだって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.26,0:23:04.61,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}因为有你在 无论身处何方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:08.75,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}何度転んでも　笑える
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:08.75,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}无论跌倒几次 我仍然微笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:13.05,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}偶然だとか　必然だとか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:13.05,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不论是偶然 还是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:16.22,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}要らないほど強く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:16.22,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}已经不需要明了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.59,0:23:20.65,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}きっと輝く思い出なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.59,0:23:20.65,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如果是闪耀的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:25.11,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君のそばにだけあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:25.11,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一定会停留在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:33.68,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\blur3}大切な世界　離さないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:33.68,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\blur3}我不会离开这珍惜的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上 能见到圣诞老人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光如果是个乖孩子 说不定能见到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 那我就做乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 粘上奶油了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光 是因为我才死的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 明天见 再想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从这边回去 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有早起怎么也习惯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑木 早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 真难得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师过来打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时都是一副这种事很麻烦的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玛雅的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 幽灵女孩子的家 去找了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 失去了孩子 被问东问西的很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 玛雅也不会放手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也说要为光做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那么执著呢 那家伙有那么温柔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很温柔呀 只是安部老师没有在看罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 她也觉得恐怕无法置身事外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是应仁之乱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和后来的战国时代有重大影响 要记好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神代 之后到办公室来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么为什么 来就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您叫我吗 安部老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样的话 没法好好谈话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜似的 乱用教师权限
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也乱用校长权限吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从昨天起 你在生什么气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我做了什么惹你生气的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样我道歉 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得 我们应该之间应该更多互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:05:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的事情 我想知道更多 作为合作伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那个女孩子可能与钥匙无关 我还是想帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 今天放学后 一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安部老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美风
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 什么呀 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学以后 有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想为昨天道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天实在是失礼了 有事想请教您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么可说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光 还在等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想偶尔也到松代外面转转 麻烦你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 请抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小布施镇 很久没来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安部老师上任以后 好像没怎么出门玩过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师有各种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让老师 更了解长野的风光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 安部老师不管什么都吃得很享受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很好呢 真想一直看下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样终于 没女朋友的日子 就要到头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天已经没戏了吧 明天再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 想问什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然问的是伤心事 想请您告诉我们小光去世时的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光虽然一直想要回家 可是一到公寓 又非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想找到帮助她的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我要是好好对待光的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈 快点 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作工作 什么都抛给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了的又不是只有你一个人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对丈夫 那是什么态度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是抱怨 就给我走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈呢 到哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光呀 今天晚上绝对不睡 等圣诞老人来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和圣诞老人说很多话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会来的吧 圣诞老人什么的就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年还有之前都来了的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不是也说 做乖孩子就能见到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在的东西就是不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也会很晚 到婶婶家里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:11:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经迟了 光在家门外等圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在学校也被人说圣诞老人不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以无论如何也想亲眼确认
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着如果找不到家在哪儿就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在外面 一直一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是她父亲 却没能了解她的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在责备自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得 承受不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起办圣诞聚会吧 为了光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呀 光在等的是圣诞老人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 现在可是夏天呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好吗 就算是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小道具就交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就决定了 明天放学后 办个开心的聚会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很开心 多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以 不来我家吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在店里 我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安部老师 真是偶然 现在回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:13:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 晚饭做多了 和我一起怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 就算你问我怎么样也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会有先约了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 算是有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一起来也不要紧 就特别招待你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没拜托你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起还有事 校长叫我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长 是关于明天拆房子的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拆房子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长的老家呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了也没什么事可做 为什么叫安部老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 果然还是 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安部老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 玛雅 好沉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去学校看了 你不在就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听主任说了 明天这个家 就要拆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:15:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种家 原以为就算没了也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是想起了各种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在院子里和父亲玩水 和朋友们烧烤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万圣节化妆 真是开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个一心埋在超自然里的父亲 我也记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后 父亲都没有回头看我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 明天要办圣诞聚会 叫上光 热热闹闹的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 拆房子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送光优先呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么 我能帮忙的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么有一件 能拜托你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.22,0:16:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呀 接下来要办个圣诞聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞老人也会来哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过一会儿圣诞老人就来了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物 给
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 圣诞夜 没能来真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来也不会在维修途中爬到背上哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才 才没那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好像见呀 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅和安部老师 到哪儿去了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险 出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是圣诞节了 玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想对圣诞老人许什么愿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呀 怪物的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙人呀 幽灵呀 UMA都能高兴地一起玩的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有呀还有呀 大家一起学习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你父亲为了保守这个约定 才建了那个学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连父亲的心意都不知道 一直只有怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有回头看的 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找出来 绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「诺查丹玛斯的钥匙」 杀害父亲的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起战斗吧 文明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:22:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超自然学院 人类 用我们的手来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立瓦尔德斯坦因学院
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.37,0:23:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是其创始者神代纯一郎 送给爱女玛雅的盛大圣诞礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.92,0:23:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中充满对逝去父亲的思念 玛雅和我重新决意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.92,0:23:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将「诺查丹玛斯的钥匙」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:23:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安部老师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.66,0:23:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅被教导主任
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.20,0:24:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.52,0:24:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世纪末超自然学院 下集 玛雅之死
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.79,0:24:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有超自然 想要守护
